<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="21">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$anthony-wu-17" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/anthony-wu-17" class="zg-link" title="Morph昊峰">Morph昊峰</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$tian-lan-yong-heng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/tian-lan-yong-heng" class="zg-link" title="天蓝永恒">天蓝永恒</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$QGBCS" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/QGBCS" class="zg-link" title="QGB CS">QGB CS</a></span>
