<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">匿名用户</h3></div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="57">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$han-chun-52" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/han-chun-52" class="zg-link" title="韩光春">韩光春</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$quan-laohu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/quan-laohu" class="zg-link" title="quan laohu">quan laohu</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="12328" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">昨天答了个烂答案，今天发现原来有过重复问题。<br>所以重定向过来，把自己的烂答案也转移过来罢。<br>知乎防重不给力，搜索不给力。<br>＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br>受邀。<br><ul><li>为什么我们知道光速不变？<br>做实验。</li><li>为什么光速不变？<br>不知道。</li><li>正经点？<br>很正经了，光速不变原理是第一性原理 [1]，不问为什么。</li></ul>[1] <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/First_principle" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">en.wikipedia.org/wiki/F</span><span class="invisible">irst_principle</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a>
<a href="/question/19580853/answer/14425884" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
